== 藥學應用 ==
亞硝酸乙酯是南非传统的以乙醇为基础的感冒和流感''药物Witdulsies''的主要成分，该药物在药房有售。它被称为传统的南非荷兰裔療法，因为同样的療法显然是由德国-荷兰阿米什人在美国發現的。但是，自1980年以来，FDA一直禁止在美国以外地区销售这种相同的药物，在美国被称为''甜亚硝酸盐''<ref name="fda">{{Cite web|title=Rulemaking History for OTC Sweet Spirits of Nitre Drug Products|url=https://www.fda.gov/Drugs/DevelopmentApprovalProcess/DevelopmentResources/Over-the-CounterOTCDrugs/StatusofOTCRulemakings/ucm072140.htm|accessdate=2016-12-26|publisher=fda.gov|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423084007/https://www.fda.gov/Drugs/DevelopmentApprovalProcess/DevelopmentResources/Over-the-CounterOTCDrugs/StatusofOTCRulemakings/ucm072140.htm}}</ref>。它的使用与致命的[[正鐵血紅蛋白血症|高铁血红蛋白血症]]有關。<ref>{{Cite web|title=ETHYL NITRITE - National Library of Medicine HSDB Database|url=https://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/a?dbs+hsdb:@term+@DOCNO+416|accessdate=2017-11-18|work=toxnet.nlm.nih.gov|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201042855/https://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/a?dbs+hsdb:@term+@DOCNO+416}}</ref>

== 對人體的毒害及危險性 ==
[[正鐵血紅蛋白血症|高鐵血红蛋白血症]]是亚硝酸乙酯的主要毒性作用。<ref name="hazmap">{{Cite web|title=Ethyl nitrite|url=https://www.haz-map.com/Agents/1476|accessdate=2020-08-08|publisher=Haz-Map|archive-date=2022-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328064704/https://www.haz-map.com/Agents/1476}}</ref>由于其高挥发性和淡淡的气味。在存在亚硝酸乙酯蒸气的情况下，很容易呼吸高剂量的亚硝酸乙酯而難以意识到，从而导致[[正鐵血紅蛋白血症|高鐵血红蛋白血症]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Proposed mechanism of nitrite-induced methemoglobinemia|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15892615/|last=Titov|first=V Yu|last2=Petrenko|first2=Yu M|journal=Biochemistry (Mosc)|issue=4|doi=10.1007/s10541-005-0139-7|year=2005|volume=70|pages=473-83|pmid=15892615|access-date=2021-03-16|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424202254/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15892615/}}</ref>，引發各輕重症狀，嚴重時可能致命。

